{
  "message": "A11y: live regions on status/summary so screen readers track progress\n\nThe bench pages have a lot of mutations during a run \u2014 iteration\ncounters tick over in #status, the summary fills in at the end.\nWithout aria-live, screen readers don't know to announce them.\n\nAdded role=\"status\" + aria-live=\"polite\" + aria-atomic=\"true\" on\nthe playground and RPC bench's #status spans, and role=\"status\" +\naria-live=\"polite\" on the summary divs so the conclusion gets read\nout when a run finishes. RPC bench's server-status banner gets the\nsame treatment, with the dot marked aria-hidden so it doesn't get\nannounced as a stray bullet.\n\nPolite (not assertive) so the announcements don't interrupt other\nscreen-reader output mid-sentence; the user controls when to hear\nthe bench results.",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "d4c763d3cc7e642fa6ac1aede09a05d6396f0225",
      "filename": "web/playground.html",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 2,
      "deletions": 2,
      "changes": 4,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/capnwasm/blob/8fff451ab36bc0dee066cf7dc0dbb2eb0aed2457/web%2Fplayground.html",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/capnwasm/raw/8fff451ab36bc0dee066cf7dc0dbb2eb0aed2457/web%2Fplayground.html",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/teamchong/capnwasm/contents/web%2Fplayground.html?ref=8fff451ab36bc0dee066cf7dc0dbb2eb0aed2457",
      "patch": "@@ -53,7 +53,7 @@ <h1>capnwasm <span class=\"dim\">playground</span></h1>\n           <option value=\"10\">10 (median)</option>\n         </select>\n       </label>\n-      <span id=\"status\"></span>\n+      <span id=\"status\" role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"></span>\n     </div>\n \n     <div id=\"results\">\n@@ -106,7 +106,7 @@ <h1>capnwasm <span class=\"dim\">playground</span></h1>\n       </div>\n     </div>\n \n-    <div id=\"summary\"></div>\n+    <div id=\"summary\" role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div>\n   </div>\n \n   <script type=\"module\" src=\"./src/playground/main.ts\"></script>"
    },
    {
      "sha": "3281f54d02328ec063c0a9f92a51a443655985ea",
